01:26:06,866 --> 01:26:17,550
propter nostram salutem descendit , incarnatus est, et homo 511 factus est, et passus est, et resurrexit tertia die, et adscendit in coelos, venturus judicare vivos et mortuos.

426
01:26:17,550 --> 01:26:33,333
Et in Spiritum sanctum. Eos autem,
